  {
    "type": "intro",
    "page": "3",
    "id": "introduction",
    "head": {
      "title": {
        "en": "INTRODUCTION",
        "zh": "简介"
      }
    },
    "notes": [
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Reporting an issue",
          "zh": "反馈问题"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Should you find an error in this manual or have a suggestion for an improvement, please consider opening an issue on GitHub (<a href=\"https://github.com/echosprint/PhysiClaw/issues\">github.com/echosprint/PhysiClaw/issues</a>). When raising an issue please include the relevant page numbers and a short description; annotated screenshots are also very welcome. We periodically update the manual based on the feedback we get.",
          "zh": "如果你发现本手册有错，或者有改进建议，欢迎到 GitHub 提交 issue（<a href=\"https://github.com/echosprint/PhysiClaw/issues\">github.com/echosprint/PhysiClaw/issues</a>）。提交时请写明相关页码，简单说一下问题，最好再附上标注过的截图。我们会根据收到的反馈定期更新手册。"
        },
        "classes": "note"
      },
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "This is just a reference",
          "zh": "这只是一份参考"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "This manual is designed to be a simple build reference. Assembling a PhysiClaw can take two to three hours, so for any section you need clarification on we recommend opening the <span class=\"ref\">.step</span> file in FreeCAD — it is often easier to follow along with the whole assembly in front of you.",
          "zh": "本手册只是一份简明的装配参考。组装 PhysiClaw 可能需要两到三个小时，所以哪一步看不明白，建议在 FreeCAD 里打开 <span class=\"ref\">.step</span> 文件——对着完整的装配体边看边装，往往会容易得多。"
        },
        "classes": "note"
      }
    ],
    "links": [
