  {
    "type": "hardware-ref",
    "page": "4",
    "id": "hardware-reference",
    "head": {
      "title": {
        "en": "HARDWARE — REFERENCE",
        "zh": "五金件 — 参考"
      }
    },
    "entries": [
      {
        "src": "fastener_11_SHCS_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Socket head cap screw (SHCS)",
          "zh": "内六角圆柱头螺钉（SHCS）"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Cylindrical head, hex drive. The default fastener for PhysiClaw.ai — used wherever the head can sit above the surface.",
          "zh": "圆柱头，用内六角扳手拧。PhysiClaw.ai 最常用的螺钉——只要螺钉头可以露在表面外，就用它。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "ISO 4762 / DIN 912",
          "zh": "ISO 4762 / DIN 912"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_10_BHCS_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Button head cap screw (BHCS)",
          "zh": "内六角盘头螺钉（BHCS）"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Domed head, hex drive. Used on surfaces where a lower profile matters but a flush head isn't required.",
          "zh": "圆顶头，用内六角扳手拧。用在既想压低高度、又不必和表面齐平的地方。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "ISO 7380-1",
          "zh": "ISO 7380-1"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_12_FHCS_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Flat head cap screw (FHCS)",
          "zh": "内六角沉头螺钉（FHCS）"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "90° countersunk head, hex drive. Sits flush with the surface — used where nothing can protrude above the part.",
          "zh": "90° 沉头，用内六角扳手拧。和表面齐平——用在不能高出零件表面的地方。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "ISO 10642 / DIN 7991",
          "zh": "ISO 10642 / DIN 7991"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_40_shim_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Shim washer",
          "zh": "垫片"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "M5 Ø8×0.5 washer. Stacked under each idler to set its axial play — measure yours, thickness varies by supplier.",
          "zh": "M5 Ø8×0.5 垫片。叠在每个惰轮下面，决定它的轴向间隙——不同供应商厚度不同，记得先量一下。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "M5 · Ø8×0.5",
          "zh": "M5 · Ø8×0.5"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_21_hex_nut_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Hex nut",
          "zh": "六角螺母"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Standard M3 hex nut, paired with a screw to clamp parts together where a T-nut won't fit.",
          "zh": "标准 M3 六角螺母。在装不下 T 型螺母的地方，用它配上螺钉把零件夹紧。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "ISO 4032 / DIN 934",
          "zh": "ISO 4032 / DIN 934"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_20_square_nut_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Square nut",
          "zh": "方螺母"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "M3 nut that sits captive in a printed pocket so it can't spin — the screw is then driven one-handed from the other side.",
          "zh": "M3 螺母，嵌在打印件的方槽里不会转——这样从另一侧单手就能拧紧螺钉。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "DIN 557",
          "zh": "DIN 557"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "hardware-ref",
    "page": "4a",
    "id": "hardware-reference-2",
    "head": {
      "title": {
        "en": "HARDWARE — REFERENCE",
        "zh": "五金件 — 参考"
      }
    },
    "entries": [
      {
        "src": "fastener_22_tnut_standard_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Extrusion T-nut (slide-in)",
          "zh": "型材 T 型螺母（端部滑入）"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Slides into a 2020 channel from the open end and locks under a screw head. Every frame-attached part rides on these.",
          "zh": "从 2020 型材的开口端滑进滑槽，被螺钉头压住卡紧。凡是装到框架上的零件，都靠它固定。"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_23_tnut_hammer_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Hammer T-nut (drop-in)",
          "zh": "锤形 T 型螺母（任意位置放入）"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Drops flat into a 2020 channel anywhere along its length, then a quarter turn locks it — no need to reach an open end.",
          "zh": "可以从 2020 滑槽的任意位置平放进去，转 90° 就卡紧——不必从型材开口端穿进来。"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_30_pulley_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "GT2 drive pulley",
          "zh": "GT2 同步带轮"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "20-tooth toothed pulley. One sits on each stepper shaft, locked to the motor's D-flat with a set screw; it drives the GT2 belt.",
          "zh": "20 齿同步带轮。每个步进电机轴上装一个，用顶丝顶在电机的 D 形扁位上，由它带动 GT2 同步带。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "GT2 · 20T",
          "zh": "GT2 · 20 齿"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_31_idler_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "GT2 idler",
          "zh": "GT2 惰轮"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Free-spinning wheel that turns the belt around the frame corners. No hub or set screw — it just guides the belt.",
          "zh": "自由转动的轮子，在框架拐角处给同步带转向。没有轮毂也没有顶丝，只负责导向。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "GT2",
          "zh": "GT2"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_32_idler_smooth_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "GT2 idler (smooth)",
          "zh": "GT2 惰轮（光面）"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Un-toothed turn wheel for the belt's flat back. Lower friction than the toothed idler where tracking isn't needed.",
          "zh": "无齿的转向轮，贴着同步带的平背面转。在不需要齿对位的地方用它，摩擦比有齿惰轮更小。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "GT2",
          "zh": "GT2"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_41_flat_bracket_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Flat bracket",
          "zh": "平板支架"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Two-hole plate with M5 holes 20 mm apart. Bolts an idler stack to the frame and ties extrusions together at a joint.",
          "zh": "两孔平板，M5 孔间距 20 mm。把惰轮组固定到框架上，也在接合处连接型材。"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "tall-left",
    "page": "4b",
    "id": "hardware-reference-3",
    "head": {
      "title": {
        "en": "HARDWARE — REFERENCE",
        "zh": "五金件 — 参考"
      }
    },
    "figures": [
      {
        "src": "fastener_50_hex_driver_assembled_cam1.svg"
      }
    ],
    "notes": [
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "2 mm hex driver",
          "zh": "2 mm 内六角扳手"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "The 2 mm hex driver will see a lot of use in this build. A quality driver is strongly recommended. Refer to the sourcing guide for suggestions.",
          "zh": "装配这台机器时，2 mm 内六角扳手会频繁用到。强烈建议备一把好用的扳手。"
        },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:152mm; top:56mm; width:120mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Driver sizes",
          "zh": "扳手规格"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "These cover the socket screws used in this build — 5 mm for M6 socket head cap screws (SHCS), 3 mm for M5 button/flat head screws (BHCS/FHCS), and 2 mm for M3 button/flat head screws.",
          "zh": "这几把扳手覆盖本次装配用到的内六角螺钉——5 mm 对应 M6 内六角圆柱头螺钉（SHCS），3 mm 对应 M5 盘头/沉头螺钉（BHCS/FHCS），2 mm 对应 M3 盘头/沉头螺钉。"
        },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:152mm; top:108mm; width:120mm;"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "printed-parts",
    "page": "5",
    "id": "printed-parts",
    "head": {
      "title": {
        "en": "3D PRINTED PARTS",
        "zh": "3D 打印件"
      }
    },
    "notesBefore": [
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Part printing settings and guidelines",
          "zh": "零件打印设置与说明"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "PhysiClaw's custom parts are printed by Selective Laser Sintering (SLS), not the common FDM. A laser fuses nylon powder in a heated powder bed, so parts come out fully solid, support-free, and strong in every direction. These parts carry side holes and overhangs: with FDM the side holes deform and the overhangs sag. Match the specifications below when sourcing parts.",
          "zh": "PhysiClaw 的定制零件用选择性激光烧结（SLS）打印，而不是常见的 FDM。激光在加热的粉末床里把尼龙粉末烧结成型，做出来的零件完全实心、不用支撑，各个方向都很结实。这些零件带有侧面的孔和悬空结构，用 FDM 打，侧孔会变形、悬空处会塌陷。采购零件时，请对照下面的规格。"
        },
        "classes": "note"
      }
    ],
    "specs": [
      {
        "k": {
          "en": "3D Printing Process",
          "zh": "3D 打印工艺"
        },
        "v": {
          "en": "Selective Laser Sintering (SLS)",
          "zh": "选择性激光烧结（SLS）"
        }
      },
      {
        "k": {
          "en": "Part Density",
          "zh": "零件密度"
        },
        "v": {
